        {
            "title": "關稅戰 | 更多中美官員日內瓦談判照釋出  雙方曾在戶外輕鬆商談",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c341c4105579fd9f8e997fe21fb01eba/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051614594192530.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中美不久前在瑞士日內瓦舉行貿易談判，其後宣佈大幅互降關稅，為期90日。\n\n</p><h2>在戶外邊走邊商談</h2>\n<p>法新社發布的照片顯示，中國副總理何立峰、中國商務部國際貿易談判代表兼副部長李成鋼、美國財政部長貝森特(Scott Bessent) 、美國貿易代表格里爾(Jamieson Greer)等出席貿易談判。期間，雙方在戶外邊走邊商談。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3454835/\">關稅戰︱中美大幅互降關稅115% 特朗普稱本周內 或與國家主席習近平通電話</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雙方代表團在戶外交談。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/55125e2581a3b2d6d50e4dbdbd10dc90/2025-05/AFP__20250514__46LW962__v1__HighRes__SwitzerlandChinaUsPoliticsDiplomacyTrade.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雙方代表團在戶外交談。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雙方代表團在戶外交談。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/277e3abffd8a776f8fc5ebda6b289485/2025-05/AFP__20250514__46LX3T2__v1__HighRes__SwitzerlandChinaUsPoliticsDiplomacyTrade.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雙方代表團在戶外交談。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雙方代表團在戶外交談。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cff2a99183defb0e670201ae881ae09/2025-05/AFP__20250514__46M37G2__v1__HighRes__SwitzerlandChinaUsPoliticsDiplomacyTrade.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雙方代表團在戶外交談。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"美國財政部長貝森特與中國副總理何立峰。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3d07dab83cfbb9aea445b4507a0eea30/2025-05/AFP__20250514__46LU8G6__v1__HighRes__SwitzerlandChinaUsPoliticsDiplomacyTrade.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美國財政部長貝森特與中國副總理何立峰。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"美國財政部長貝森特與中國副總理何立峰。法新社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d1c3117b8dfef1476c14cbd780aa86f0/2025-05/AFP__20250514__46LV2G2__v1__HighRes__SwitzerlandChinaUsPoliticsDiplomacyTrade.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美國財政部長貝森特與中國副總理何立峰。法新社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>中美雙方星期一（12日）發表聯合聲明，承諾自14日起互降此前加征的高關稅，維持90日，並表明將繼續就經貿關係進行協商。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-politics/3455400/\">關稅戰︱中美談判圖片曝光 何立峰露齒笑貝森特略拘謹</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
