            "title": "中美關稅戰︱不受影響　《職業特工隊：最終清算》月底中國上畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9775f01a7a14d76d5db02e12d9bd1fbb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051614155735395.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>彭博社：據知情人士透露，派拉蒙環球出品的動作片，由美國動作影星湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise）主演的《職業特工隊：最終清算》(「Mission: Impossible – The Final Reckoning」內地譯名：《碟中諜8：最終清算》)已獲得中國方面批准，將於5月30日上映。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"《職業特工隊：最終清算》海報。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2985b65feefa9dd439b92caad944c239/2025-05/0516001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《職業特工隊：最終清算》海報。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3446026/%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%B1%80%E9%81%A9%E5%BA%A6%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F\" onclick=\"\" oncontextmenu=\"\">關稅︱國家電影局：適度減少美國影片進口數量</a>\n</p>\n<p>報道表示，此舉表明，中美貿易緊張局勢並未對好萊塢造成任何顯著的報復。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
